title: 70-Ohm short on PP3V3_G3H (820-00928)
message:
I'm a bit of a rush with this one. 

2017 15" MacBook Pro board (820-00928) stuck at 5V. I found a 60-70 Ohm short to ground on PP3V3_G3H. When I inject 3.3V into PP3V3_G3H (after removal of fuse R6923), I get 20V on all ports. But the current is only around 100mA, not enough to heat up any component. How do I find the short on PP3V3_G3H?
